\[Kappa]H + \[Sigma]H)*Sinh(\[CapitalSigma]*\[Chi]Heff))*(2*\[Chi]Leff*Cosh(\
\[CapitalSigma]*\[Chi]Leff) + (2*\[Kappa]T + \[Sigma]L)*Sinh(\[CapitalSigma]*\
